title: Noumin Kanren no Skill bakka Agetetara Naze ka Tsuyoku Natta.
description: To live from bottom-class to top-class farmer, our protagonist Aru Wayn levelled up his agricultural skills, and sometimes his other skills leveled up as well by helping out his friends. One day, when his last skill level hit MAX, his life changes."I want to live as a normal farmer!!"
